, in good agreement with previous results in literature, and derive\ndata-driven lower-bounds based on the non-parametric modelling of the halo\ndensity. The outcome of our broad study stands out as a representative of the\nstate-of-the-art in the field, and falls within the interest of current and\nfuture experimental collaborations involved in DM indirect detection programs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2018 17:43:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Dec 2018 16:11:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-21"}
