\ndecreased from Cycle 21 to Cycle 24. It means that both the toroidal and\npoloidal components and therefore, the solar global magnetic field decreased\nfrom Cycle 21 to Cycle 24.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2018 21:02:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 May 2018 11:22:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
