ears to be superior. The\nproposed procedure is then applied to patients who suffered a stroke and were\nreleased from rehabilitation facilities either to skilled nursing facilities or\nto their homes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Apr 2018 04:25:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 02:11:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2018 01:11:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-22"}
