\nvariance unexplained, which complies with the expected range from the\nsensitivity analysis. Our new off-axis PSF modelling method lays the\nground-work for testing on-sky in the near future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Apr 2018 09:40:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-17"}
